        p Zombies epidemic! Again there are two variants of actors: #[code Living] and #[code Dead]. The dead chase the living - the living run for their lives. They also flock together to find safty in numbers - the fools! When a zombie bites the living - they turn into a zombie. Note that zombies move with the same speed as the living - neither can outrun the other. So if you stay far from danger, you should be safe... or should you? Do you think anyone will survive this? Watch and see for your self!


